reviews.title: Won\'t work!
reviews.comment: Will not work on my phone the runs Jelly Bean. Contacted the theme designer and they will not email back with a fix. EXTREMELY DISAPPOINTED and want what I paid for.

reviews.title: Clean-looking
reviews.comment: I really like this theme. I was looking for a theme with a 3D popout look for the convo bubbles and this is perfect. I wish you could change the green part of the theme with another color though.
reviews.author: A Google User
